summary: As an independent translator Dutch-Polish/Polish-Dutch I work directly for individual customers. I offer sworn translations as well as not-sworn translations both into Dutch and Polish. I specialize in legal documents (family law, estate). As an accomplished legal translator I work for the Dutch administration of justice. I am also a court interpreter.
